### **Reason and Rationality:**

66. "Reason is the only means of survival, the only guide to knowledge, and the only tool for understanding reality."
67. "The truth is not for all men, but only for those who seek it."
68. "Man’s mind is his basic tool of survival."
69. "If any civilization is to survive, it is the morality of altruism that men have to reject."
